These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, climbing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is not the person drinking soy-milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | tea    | coffee    | soy-milk |
| Sport      | rowing | badminton | climbing | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, tea, coffee
There 4 different types of food: banana, nectarine, blueberry, strawberry
1. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person eating nectarine##6
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking water##1
8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | tea    | water | coffee    |
| Food       | strawberry | nectarine | blueberry  | banana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, soy-milk, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, chef, architect, social-worker
1. the person drinking mirinda is not the freelancer##6
2. the chef is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
3. the architect is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the chef is the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the chef##1
6. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
7. the freelancer is on the far left or far right##3
8. the architect is somewhere to the left of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | iced-tea  | cola  | soy-milk |
| Job        | architect | social-worker | chef | freelancer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, dog, mouse, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, van, jet-ski, helicopter
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is not the owner of the dog##6
4. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the van##1
6. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | dog | mouse | turtle     | frog |
| Transport   | van     | jet-ski    | motorbike | helicopter    |

