.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, lemonade, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, scooter, roller
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person driving the roller##6
5. the person driving the train is not the person drinking water##6
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | water        | tea | lemonade | soy-milk |
| Transport   | roller | train | ship     | scooter   |

