.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, comedy, zombie, adventure
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, chinese, japanese
1. the malaysian is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is not the turkish##6
3. the malaysian is on the far right##1
4. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
8. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
9. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | zombie    | musical  | adventure   |
| Nationality   | chinese  | japanese | turkish | malaysian |

