.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, thriller, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, house, blues, pop
1. the fan blues is on the left or right of the fan trance##3
2. the fan blues is not the person watching disaster movies##6
3. the person watching satire movies is the fan house##1
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the fan pop##3
5. the fan blues is on the far left##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is the fan trance##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the fan trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | disaster     | thriller | satire |
| Music-Genre   | blues | trance | pop      | house         |

