.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, water, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, software-developer, nurse, project-manager
1. the teacher is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
3. the project-manager is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
6. the teacher is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking sprite is not the project-manager##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | sprite  | juice        | water      | fanta          |
| Job        | teacher | software-developer | project-manager | nurse |

