The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, snowmobile, trike
1. the librarian is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the van is not the project-manager##6
3. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
4. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the trike is the social-worker##1
7. the librarian is not the person driving the trike##6
8. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | librarian  | social-worker | project-manager    | police-officer |
| Transport   | van | trike | snowmobile | taxi  |

