.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, frog, guinea-pig, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, tennis, cycling
1. the person who's sport is sailing is not the owner of the rat##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
6. the person who's sport is basketball is not the owner of the frog##6
7. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | rat        | horse  | frog     |
| Sport   | sailing     | cycling | basketball | tennis |

