.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, photography, baking, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, reggae, d&b, dubstep
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the fan reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
3. the fan d&b is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
4. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan dubstep and the person who's hobby is baking##2
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the fan reggae is between the fan rock and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | baking | photography    | filmmaking | writing |
| Music-Genre   | rock         | reggae | dubstep   | d&b     |

