.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pineapple, lemon, cabbage
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, scooter, train, van
1. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
2. the person eating cabbage is not the person driving the subway##6
3. the person driving the scooter is the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person driving the train is not the person eating cabbage##6
6. the person eating pineapple is not the person driving the subway##6
7. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
8. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | orange  | lemon | pineapple | cabbage |
| Transport   | train | subway     | van     | scooter    |

