.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, papaya, pumpkin, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, thriller, mystery, comedy
1. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5
2. the person eating papaya is not the person watching thriller movies##6
3. the person eating cauliflower is the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating papaya and the person watching crime movies##2
6. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | radish | papaya      | cauliflower | pumpkin   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | mystery | comedy   | crime |

