2. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | juice       | coffee | cola     | iced-tea     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | epic       | thriller | drama |

