4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is between the firefighter and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the firefighter is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
7. the software-developer is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | teacher  | designer | software-developer | firefighter |
| Sport   | sailing | swimming | soccer   | parkour |

