1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's hobby is puzzles##6
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | photography | sudoku | puzzles | filmmaking |
| Pet     | turtle  | rat      | guinea-pig  | hedgehog       |

