.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, fanta, cola
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, boat, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the bus is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
6. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | sprite | cola      | fanta   |
| Transport   | motorbike  | taxi   | boat | bus |

 